# Joo Navigation

Read order:

1. user-provided exact files
2. `rules/context-navigation.md`
3. `AI_INDEX.md`
4. file-level `@ai-*` headers
5. relevant source files
6. relevant tests
7. broader search only if needed

Report only files read, reason, next target, and uncertainty.
